article_title: A.C. casino tax plan languishes in Legislature
article_text: We have used your information to see if you have a subscription with us. So far we have not found one. If you feel you are currently subscribed please click on the button to attempt to find your account.

og.description: Three months after it was introduced in Trenton, a plan to transform the way Atlantic City casinos pay property taxes continues to languish in the Legislature, where it remains tabled despite bipartisan support from Atlantic County officials.
